headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Introducing: Tale Of Us
content:
Italy’s finest purveyors of lush melodic techno, Tale Of Us are now available for hire as a resident DJ in your nightclub – watch out for the call from English Dave, you’ll need to secure transport to pick them up. You can also check out your Nightclub’s office computer for more information and use it to book the resident DJ you’d like performing at your club at any time.

And don’t forget to dial into Los Santos Underground Radio to hear Solomun’s latest set.
